# Quick Start

### 1. Start the peer
```javascript
await ZYNQ.peer.start();
```

### 2. Listen for readiness
```javascript
ZYNQ.peer.on('ready', id => {
  console.log('My ID:', id);
});
```

### 3. Connect to another peer
```javascript
await ZYNQ.peer.connect('peer-id');
```

### 4. Send a message
```javascript
ZYNQ.peer.sendTo('peer-id', 'Hello world');
```

### 5. Listen for messages
```javascript
ZYNQ.peer.on('message', ({ peerId, message }) => {
  console.log(peerId, message);
});
```
